# Shared Scripts & Utilities

The [src/scripts/utils/](mdc:src/scripts/utils) directory contains shared utility modules used across the desktop environment and app modules.

## Key Files
- [boot.js](mdc:src/scripts/utils/boot.js): Handles boot animation, login, and session state.
- [menuBar.js](mdc:src/scripts/utils/menuBar.js): Shared menu bar logic for all apps.
- [toolbar.js](mdc:src/scripts/utils/toolbar.js): Shared toolbar logic for all apps.
- [eventBus.js](mdc:src/scripts/utils/eventBus.js): Global event bus for inter-component communication.
- [programRegistry.js](mdc:src/scripts/utils/programRegistry.js): Registers and manages app modules.
- [iframePreloader.js](mdc:src/scripts/utils/iframePreloader.js): Preloads app iframes for smoother UX.
- [tooltip.js](mdc:src/scripts/utils/tooltip.js): Tooltip logic for UI elements.
- [login.js](mdc:src/scripts/utils/login.js): Handles login UI and logic.
- [common.js](mdc:src/scripts/utils/common.js): Common actions (e.g., window exit) for all apps.

## Usage
- App modules and core scripts import these utilities for consistent UI, event handling, and app management.
- For menu bars, toolbars, and common actions, always use the shared setup functions from this directory.

